about IRS abuses, was fired a day after a new IRS chief, also in
congressional testimony, says no whistleblowers will be fired. The
woman is quickly reinstated by him and her supervisors temporarily
suspended. By David Cay Johnston.
</P>
<P>
   MINN-VENTURA (St. Paul) _ In his first three months of office,
