<HEADLINE>
COMPETITION SPURS HOSPITALS TOWARD ALL PRIVATE ROOMS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Ill., Ark., Calif., Fla., N.J., Ohio)  (Eds: Also will move in `a' category.) 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(mk) 
