u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GRAPHICS-WEEKEND-BUDG     04-17 0291
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-WEEKEND-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the New York Times News Service Macintosh graphics
scheduled for Sunday, 04-18-99. They are available to all NYT
