<HEADER>
A2654 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-KOSOVO-REBE     04-17 0035
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-KOSOVO-REBELS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-REBELS (Skopje, Macedonia) will not move in tonight's New
York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service, Apr. 17.
</P>
