<P>
   NATO-OPINION _ WASHINGTON _ For many Poles, gaining membership
in NATO has been a dream fulfilled. A Polish journalist working in
the United States gives us his thoughts and feelings on Poland
becoming a member of NATO this year along with Hungary and the
Czech Republic. (Weglarczyk, Cox News Service). 18.
